OL,3,CReform Senedd candidate resigns
OL,4,Caccusing party of 'betrayal'
OL,6,FA Reform UK Senedd candidate has
OL,7,Fresigned from the party saying that it
OL,8,Fhas "betrayed its early members'
OL,9,Fvision" and criticising the selection
OL,10,Fprocess.
OL,12,FPatrick Benham-Crosswell was standing
OL,13,Fin the Gwyr Abertawe constituency for
OL,14,FReform UK in the 2026 Senedd election.
OL,16,FIn a statement posted on his Facebook
OL,17,Fpage on Saturday (28 March) afternoon,
OL,18,Fhe announced he was resigning from the
OL,19,Fparty, saying "Reform has left him".
OL,26,@uD@Is{
