OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1774890348
OL,3,CReform Senedd candidate resigns
OL,4,Caccusing party of 'betrayal'
OL,6,FHe added: "Reform has sunk deep into
OL,7,Fthe sewer when it should have been a
OL,8,Fbeacon of decency."
OL,10,FPatrick Benham-Crosswell was ranked
OL,11,Ffifth in the Gwyr Abertawe
OL,12,Fconstituency. Francesca O'Brien, who
OL,13,Fdefected from the Conservatives last
OL,14,Fyear, is top of the list.
OL,16,FHe claimed that "across Wales the
OL,17,Fcandidate appointment does not reflect
OL,18,Fhow people performed in the selection
OL,19,Fprocess; I know because I was there."
OL,26,@sD@Os{
