OL,3,CReform Senedd candidate resigns
OL,4,Caccusing party of 'betrayal'
OL,6,F"In many constituencies those at the
OL,7,Ftop of the list are not the best. Far
OL,8,Ftoo many are Tories ` and the Reform
OL,9,Fvote will suffer," he added.
OL,11,FMr Benham-Crosswell is the second
OL,12,FReform UK candidate to stand down
OL,13,Fsince the party released a full list
OL,14,Fof candidates for the 2026 Senedd
OL,15,Felections on Wednesday 25 March.
