PN,46704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1774890348
OL,3,CReform Senedd candidate resigns
OL,4,Caccusing party of 'betrayal'
OL,6,FCorey Edwards, who was first on the
OL,7,Flist in Pen-y-Bont Bro Morgannwg,
OL,8,Fstood down on Friday citing his mental
OL,9,Fhealth. It came after photos of him
OL,10,Fappearing to strike a Nazi salute
OL,11,Femerged online.
OL,13,FMr Benham-Crosswell concluded his post
OL,14,Fon Facebook by saying: "The Reform
OL,15,FParty has betrayed its early members'
OL,16,Fvision, labour and achievements. I
OL,17,Fwon't be a party to that, so I resign."
OL,19,FReform UK has been contacted for a
OL,20,Fcomment.
